Alias       MyK+   K+
Alias       MyK-   K-
Alias       MyPi-  pi-
Alias       MyPi+  pi+

ChargeConj  MyK+   MyK-
ChargeConj  MyPi-  MyPi+
#
Decay B0sig
  1.000        MyK+       MyPi-            PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay anti-B0sig
##
Decay MyK+
  1.000         mu+       nu_mu            PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay MyK-
#
Decay MyPi-
  1.000         mu-       anti-nu_mu       PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay MyPi+
End
